{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"d8f65916-e214-43d0-b66d-1496a397bb58","content":"`.testsettings` files are **legacy** and ignored by modern MSTest (v3+). You need to migrate to a `.runsettings` file. Here's your configuration mapped:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout=30000` | `<TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>` in `<MSTest>` |\n| `AssemblyResolution` / `useLoadContext` | Not needed (modern test host handles this) |\n| Code Coverage `DataCollector` | `<DataCollectors>` in `<DataCollectionRunSettings>` |\n\nLet me create the equivalent `.runsettings` file:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01F6pc9fvbZ4RNnc5oxskcM8","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating .runsettings file"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01EJBTbnu8ZgUXYvzN7UAPu4","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-282b3ffe514544c8ada236f804258834/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://Microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.CoverageCollectorDataCollector, Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector, Culture=neutral\" />\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-282b3ffe514544c8ada236f804258834/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"f8c8b227-7c37-4b41-8ddb-937af8aa5dcc","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file which is a legacy format. Modern MSTest (v3+) uses `.runsettings` files instead. Let me explain the migration and create the equivalent `.runsettings` file.\n\nThe `.testsettings` file has:\n1. Assembly resolution with `useLoadContext=\"true\"` — not needed in modern MS